OL,3,CWorld Cup fans grab free tickets due
OL,4,Cto Fifa checkout error
OL,6,FAround 60 football fans were able to
OL,7,Fbag themselves free tickets to the
OL,8,FWorld Cup this summer due to a glitch
OL,9,Fon the Fifa website - and have now
OL,10,Fbeen told to pay up.
OL,12,FAn online error caused the tickets,
OL,13,Fall of which were for group stage
OL,14,Fgames in Toronto, to be valued at 0 US
OL,15,Fdollars during the checkout process.
OL,17,FBut Fifa has now given the fans seven
OL,18,Fdays to pay the full price for their
OL,19,Ftickets, or they will be removed from
OL,20,Ftheir accounts.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
