OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780689960
OL,3,CWorld Cup fans grab free tickets due
OL,4,Cto Fifa checkout error
OL,6,F"Fifa can confirm that approximately
OL,7,F60 Fifa World Cup 2026 fans received a
OL,8,Fcommunication on Wednesday, 3 June
OL,9,Fregarding tickets that had been
OL,10,Fallocated at no charge (0 USD) due to
OL,11,Fa prior payment issue during the
OL,12,Fcheckout process," a spokesperson for
OL,13,Fthe international football association
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,F"The tickets requested by these fans
OL,17,Fremain reserved, and the affected fans
OL,18,Fhave been invited to complete payment
OL,19,Fof the correct amount. Fifa regrets
OL,20,Fthe error and any inconvenience
OL,21,Fcaused."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
