OL,3,CWorld Cup fans grab free tickets due
OL,4,Cto Fifa checkout error
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FTickets for the World Cup are still on
OL,12,Fsale as the teams prepare to kick off
OL,13,Fthe tournament in the US and Mexico
OL,14,Fnext week.
OL,16,FFifa has faced a barrage of criticism
OL,17,Fover the prices of tickets for the
OL,18,Ffinals and its decision to adopt a
OL,19,Fdynamic pricing strategy, which has
OL,20,Fseen costs fluctuate.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
