OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780689960
OL,3,CWorld Cup fans grab free tickets due
OL,4,Cto Fifa checkout error
OL,6,FThe association has also set up an
OL,7,Fofficial resale platform, where it
OL,8,Ftakes 15 per cent cuts from the seller
OL,9,Fand the buyer of each ticket.
OL,11,FFifa's president Gianni Infantino said
OL,12,Fthe prices being charged were
OL,13,Fjustified in the North American market.
OL,15,F"We are in the market in which
OL,16,Fentertainment is the most developed in
OL,17,Fthe world. So we have to apply market
OL,18,Frates," Infantino said at a conference
OL,19,Fin Beverly Hills.
