OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780689960
OL,3,CWorld Cup fans grab free tickets due
OL,4,Cto Fifa checkout error
OL,6,FAttorneys general of New York and New
OL,7,FJersey launched an investigation into
OL,8,Fthe association's ticketing practices
OL,9,Flast month after fans cited
OL,10,Fcomplaints, including claims they were
OL,11,Fmisled about the location of their
OL,12,Fseats.
OL,14,FThe final will be held at the 82,000-
OL,15,Fseat MetLife Stadium, in New York,
OL,16,Fwith secondary seat seller SeatGeek
OL,17,Flisting tickets starting from $7,869
OL,18,F(#5,852), all the way up to $68,457
OL,19,F(#50,912), depending on where fans sit.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
