CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780689960
OL,3,CWorld Cup fans grab free tickets due
OL,4,Cto Fifa checkout error
OL,6,FLetitia James, for New York, claimed
OL,7,FFifa had turned ticket sales into a
OL,8,F"gauntlet of confusion, fake scarcity,
OL,9,Fand impossibly high prices".
OL,11,F"New Yorkers have been waiting years
OL,12,Ffor the World Cup to come to their
OL,13,Fbackyard, and they deserve a fair shot
OL,14,Fat affordable tickets," James said in
OL,15,Fa statement on May 27.
OL,17,F"No one should be manipulated into
OL,18,Fpaying sky-high prices for seats, and
OL,19,Ffans should be able to trust that the
OL,20,Ftickets they purchase will be the ones
OL,21,Fthey receive."
